To summarize, there is a trade-off between lowering the peak level of infectious people on the one hand, and reducing fatalities as well as economic losses on the other hand. If the main goal is to lower the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
